    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The American Federation OF\nLabor has sent letters broadcast\nover the country asking the unions\naffiliated to furnish the sinews OF\nwar in the big fight that is ap-\npreaching for representation in\ncongress by men who are fair to\nthe common people and who will\nsee something other than the in\nterests of organized capital. The\nletter states that the demands for\nfair trea tment made by the fedora\nton on congress have been ignored\nand that there is nothing that can\nbe done except to get out and fight\nuntil conditions are bettered. 1t is\nbelieved that liberal response will\nbe made by local unions to the re-\nquest for funds with which to car\nry on the fight."
    }
  ]
